com.unvired.login
Interface LoginListener

public interface LoginListener

If the application is connecting to the server for login this interface has to be implemented.This Protocol notifies about the result of the login process.

Method Summary

loginSuccessful

void loginSuccessful()
Notifies that the username and password combination entered by the user is correct. This method is called in response to successive logins after the initial authentication. This is the preferred point in your code for placing the application specific logic.
